    "description": "An M5 feature-family template carries a Stable (or LTS) public claim only when its scorecard template and compatibility-packet template are both complete, all required sections are published, the proof packet is current within its freshness SLO, any waiver is unexpired, and the owner is signed off. A family that loses any of those must drop below the cutline rather than inherit an adjacent green family."
